\" style=\"color:#00b3f2;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Colors</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-cd91c5bd-bec2-457c-b646-ec124e39e163\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b474beae-ac2a-4dd0-a3ff-79f0223a9467\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">서체와 함께 CI를 이루는 요수 중에 가장 중요한것은 컬러입니다. 그  색상은 그 이미지와 매칭이 되는 컬러를 많이 선책하고 대표될 수 있는 색상으로 내세워야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a355478f-3d16-4b4c-8c80-b215cb37abef\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2f8449e6-de75-4f79-bea3-1e00c797f8dd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-2f8449e6-de75-4f79-bea3-1e00c797f8dd\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMTdfNDYg/MDAxNjY4Njg0MzQ5MTY0.iewmRbGK2wDg3KPK_tHNkhqUn8dvQGPsTdIowVv0g0Ig.yQ_A8j3ljXCARMbdi4ZQMVL2yUayv4qntP33W9uWV8Yg.PNG.cookthedesign/01_CI_%EC%9D%B4%EC%9D%8C%EA%B1%B4%EC%84%A4.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3105\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2396\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMTdfNDYg/MDAxNjY4Njg0MzQ5MTY0.iewmRbGK2wDg3KPK_tHNkhqUn8dvQGPsTdIowVv0g0Ig.yQ_A8j3ljXCARMbdi4ZQMVL2yUayv4qntP33W9uWV8Yg.PNG.cookthedesign/01_CI_%EC%9D%B