e-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-78f2f0fb-a024-4ab3-9a1b-0dec381ca1f6\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMTdfMTE1/MDAxNjY4NjgyNzk5ODgy.5euM3oRNMA-x40Obz5dr51ogHnwbPJTIyr8ExJLBLh8g.e-yYoK1qpB0sWieY9ho-cC_Tf8ImrQhNeO6-1WQPzmEg.PNG.cookthedesign/Untitled-1.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"6512\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2953\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMTdfMTE1/MDAxNjY4NjgyNzk5ODgy.5euM3oRNMA-x40Obz5dr51ogHnwbPJTIyr8ExJLBLh8g.e-yYoK1qpB0sWieY9ho-cC_Tf8ImrQhNeO6-1WQPzmEg.PNG.cookthedesign/Untitled-1.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-71bf5e2f-1ec6-4c3a-9512-39594cc123c5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eec95bc6-0f11-4643-a885-711a9f84afb5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2f229696-2851-47f5-ade2-07b0cfa29c4f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>흔히 사이트에 나와 있는 일본 색채연구소의 자료입니다. 오래된 자료이긴 하지만 굉장히 형용사 문구를 접목한 소중한 자료라고 판단됩니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bf3244c1-9b55-472f-9b7a-c2ae7d475e68\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3f793db7-715f-4f85-b19a-163032cd5579\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-3f793db7-715f-4f85-b19a-163032cd5579\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMTdfMTU2/MDAxNjY4NjgzODc5NjE5.we7B4XeiTSn6VasQGoAxvt-uU_txbzh3jFzIJdZ2Qokg.1t0Oe80WgXeGMgaFkW-cLe7Htg4eVXfJ4pDvN1nwB3Ug.PNG.cookthedesign/01_CI_%EC%9D%B4%EC%9D%8C%EA%B1%B4%EC%84%A4.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1036\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1035\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMTdfMTU2/MDAxNjY4NjgzODc5NjE5.we7B4XeiTSn6VasQGoAxvt-uU_txbzh3jFzIJdZ2Qokg.1t0Oe80WgXeGMgaFkW-cLe7Htg4eVXfJ4pDvN1nwB3Ug.PNG.cookthedesign/01_CI_%EC%9D%B4%EC%9D%8C%EA%B1%B4%EC%84%A4.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5f7a6282-7930-4064-81e6-4a5f4cc78371\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-75285c25-61e4-4dc4-9266-6498976a133b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-172eed13-3716-49ba-9d26-322adfe43896\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>여러분은 위의 컬러는 보면 어떤 기업이 떠오르시나요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-590e5b1f-741f-4435-9ade-60a5bd79b89b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c22ee529-3493-43c9-ac3c-52326feb192a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>이처럼 그 기업의 브랜드컬러는 기업의 성공과 더불어 기업의 얼굴이 될 수 있는 매력적인 요소를 내포하고 있습니다. 물론 대표적인 기업의 성공이 전제되야 하겠지만 쇼핑몰이나 사업 운영시에 기업의 색상만으로 그 기업을 떠올린다는것은 정말로 매력적인 일이 아닐 수 없습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-688102ec-4243-4924-a5b3-04241ca605f9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e303f94b-03c1-4e3a-86ce-1529cc9fc0ed\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ff3102b0-dc2f-4784-abd2-8dde514b454d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-28f27bcb-dc62-4f51-a8c3-fce25891d3da\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-6eb65ee3-ef27-4fc4-9ef1-214b5fb35357\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bceb3f42-af28-41af-a2bf-c6edf4734534\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-42edf0c1-9d49-4fff-b701-350f89971cbc\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>대표적인 기업 브랜드 컬러</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a3afd12f-106f-473b-bccf-c41badc31922\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-a3afd12f-106f-473b-bccf-c41badc31922\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMTdfMTk1/MDAxNjY4NjgzNzc1Mjc1.ASlE7htY7T_